<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von Golden
                            <expan>Gensin<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>jüdin<ex>n</ex></expan>, und der <expan>Secklin<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>jüdin<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>wegen bey uns</add> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> selbs
                                <expan>bottsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> kurczlich
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, daz ir das in gut
                        von uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> wellet. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dienst und
                            <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>walp<ex>ur</ex>gis</expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula">
<ab>Cettula <expan>int<ex>er</ex>clusa</expan>: <expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, auch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> botten den
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sigelten</expan> brief, den ir uns zu lesen geschikt
                        habt, <expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.</ab>
